description: Best practices for using @inquirer/prompts in CLI applications
globs: **/*.{ts,js}
---

- Use async/await for handling prompts to improve readability
- Validate user input with custom validation functions
- Implement default values for common user inputs
- Use the `when` condition to conditionally show prompts
- Group related prompts together for better user experience
